# BidPazar Web Project Brief

## Core Tech Stack
- Next.js 15.2+
- React 19+
- TypeScript
- TailwindCSS
- Socket.io Client
- Simple-Peer WebRTC

## Key Components
- User authentication and account management
- Product marketplace browsing
- Live auction streaming and participation
- Real-time bidding interface
- Live chat during streams
- Private messaging between users
- Admin dashboard
- Payment processing

## Frontend Architecture
- Next.js App Router for routing
- React components with TypeScript
- TailwindCSS for styling
- React Hook Form for form management
- Zod for validation
- Axios for API requests
- Socket.io for real-time updates
- HLS.js and simple-peer for media streaming

## Pages/Routes
- Home/landing
- Authentication (sign-in, sign-up)
- Product listings and details
- Live stream browser and viewer
- Dashboard for users
- Admin panel
- Messaging interface
- Static pages (About, Terms, FAQ)

## Integration Points
- Backend REST API
- WebSocket server
- WebRTC streaming
- Payment processing

- Notifications system